Class Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.dynamodb.model.Key
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Deprecated. 
    This class is no longer supported by the latest service API.

    @Deprecated
public class Key
extends Object
implements Serializable

    The primary key that uniquely identifies each item in a table. A primary key can be a one attribute (hash) primary key or a two attribute (hash-and-range) primary key.
